N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 2651.1 - Definitions

State Regulations
(a) Commissioner
shall mean the New York State Commissioner of Housing and Community

Renewal. (b) Construction shall
mean construction, reconstruction, alteration, addition, conversion or
rehabilitation of multiple dwellings. (c) Division shall mean the New York State

Division of Housing and Community Renewal. Notes
